{
    "poem_title": "L’IMPÉNITENT",
    "author": "Paul Verlaine",
    "structure": "",
    "year": "1889",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "RÔDEUR vanné, ton œil fané",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Tout plein d’un désir satané",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Mais qui n’est pas l’œil d’un bélître.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Quand passe quelqu’un de gentil",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Lance un éclair comme une vitre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "RÔDEUR vanné, ton œil fané\nTout plein d’un désir satané\nMais qui n’est pas l’œil d’un bélître.\nQuand passe quelqu’un de gentil\nLance un éclair comme une vitre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Ton blaire flaire, âpre et subtil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et l’étamine et le pistil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Toute fleur, tout fruit, toute viande,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et la langue d’homme entendu",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Pourlèche ta lèvre friande.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ton blaire flaire, âpre et subtil,\nEt l’étamine et le pistil,\nToute fleur, tout fruit, toute viande,\nEt la langue d’homme entendu\nPourlèche ta lèvre friande."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Vieux faune en l’air guettant ton dû,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "As-tu vraiment bandé, tendu",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "L’arme assez de tes paillardises ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "L’as-tu, drôle, braquée assez ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ce n’est rien que tu nous le dises.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vieux faune en l’air guettant ton dû,\nAs-tu vraiment bandé, tendu\nL’arme assez de tes paillardises ?\nL’as-tu, drôle, braquée assez ?\nCe n’est rien que tu nous le dises."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Quoi, malgré ces reins fricassés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ce cœur éreinté, tu ne sais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Que dévouer à la luxure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ton cœur, tes reins, ta poche à fiel,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ta rate et toute ta fressure !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quoi, malgré ces reins fricassés,\nCe cœur éreinté, tu ne sais\nQue dévouer à la luxure\nTon cœur, tes reins, ta poche à fiel,\nTa rate et toute ta fressure !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sucrés et doux comme le miel,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Damnants comme le feu du ciel,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Bleus comme fleur, noirs comme poudre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Tu raffoles beaucoup des yeux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "De tout genre en dépit du Foudre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sucrés et doux comme le miel,\nDamnants comme le feu du ciel,\nBleus comme fleur, noirs comme poudre,\nTu raffoles beaucoup des yeux\nDe tout genre en dépit du Foudre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Les nez te plaisent, gracieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Ou simplement malicieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Étant la force des visages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Étant aussi,’suivant des gens,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Des indices et des présages.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les nez te plaisent, gracieux\nOu simplement malicieux\nÉtant la force des visages,\nÉtant aussi,’suivant des gens,\nDes indices et des présages."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Longs baisers plus clairs que des chants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Tout petits baisers astringents",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on dirait qui vous sucent l’âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Bons gros baisers d’enfants, légers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Baisers danseurs, telle une flamme.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Longs baisers plus clairs que des chants,\nTout petits baisers astringents\nQu’on dirait qui vous sucent l’âme,\nBons gros baisers d’enfants, légers\nBaisers danseurs, telle une flamme."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Baisers mangeurs, baisers mangés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Baisers buveurs, bus, enragés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Baisers languides et farouches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Ce que t’aimes bien, c’est surtout,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "N’est-ce pas ? les belles boubouches.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Baisers mangeurs, baisers mangés,\nBaisers buveurs, bus, enragés,\nBaisers languides et farouches,\nCe que t’aimes bien, c’est surtout,\nN’est-ce pas ? les belles boubouches."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Les corps enfin sont de ton goût,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Mieux pourtant couchés que debout,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Se mouvant sur place qu’en marche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Mais de n’importe quel climat,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Pont-Saint-Esprit ou Pont-de-l’Arche.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les corps enfin sont de ton goût,\nMieux pourtant couchés que debout,\nSe mouvant sur place qu’en marche,\nMais de n’importe quel climat,\nPont-Saint-Esprit ou Pont-de-l’Arche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Pour que ce goût les acclamât",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Minces, grands d’aspect plutôt mat,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Faudrait pourtant du jeune en somme.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Pieds fins et forts, tout légers bras",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Musculeux et des cheveux comme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour que ce goût les acclamât\nMinces, grands d’aspect plutôt mat,\nFaudrait pourtant du jeune en somme.\nPieds fins et forts, tout légers bras\nMusculeux et des cheveux comme"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Ça tombe, longs, bouclés ou ras, –",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Sinon pervers et scélérats",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Tout à fait, un peu d’innocence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "En moins, pour toi sauver, du moins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Quelque ombre encore do décence ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ça tombe, longs, bouclés ou ras, –\nSinon pervers et scélérats\nTout à fait, un peu d’innocence\nEn moins, pour toi sauver, du moins,\nQuelque ombre encore do décence ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Nenni do ! Vous, soyez témoins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Dieux la connaissant dans les coins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Que ces manières de parts telles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Sont pour s’amuser mieux au fond",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Sans trop musser aux bagatelles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nenni do ! Vous, soyez témoins,\nDieux la connaissant dans les coins,\nQue ces manières de parts telles,\nSont pour s’amuser mieux au fond\nSans trop musser aux bagatelles."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "C’est ainsi que les choses vont",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Et que les raillards fieffés font.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Mais tu te ris de ces morales, –",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Tel un quelqu’un plus que pressé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Passe outre aux défenses murales !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est ainsi que les choses vont\nEt que les raillards fieffés font.\nMais tu te ris de ces morales, –\nTel un quelqu’un plus que pressé\nPasse outre aux défenses murales !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Et tu réponds, un peu lassé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "De te voir ainsi relancé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "De ta voix que la soif dégrade",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Mais qui n’est pas d’un marmiteux :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "« Qu’y peux-tu faire, camarade,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et tu réponds, un peu lassé\nDe te voir ainsi relancé,\nDe ta voix que la soif dégrade\nMais qui n’est pas d’un marmiteux :\n« Qu’y peux-tu faire, camarade,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Si nous sommes cet amiteux ? »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si nous sommes cet amiteux ? »"
        }
